ilwX.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	看，這就是武士道\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/oRCg4BC8w44M5Yg5B4fB5TefmG5R4r.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/oRCg4BC8w44M5Yg5B4fB5TefmG5R4r.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	拍電影，用真人\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/G0F5t66F6CxC830xLii032i3kfb6X6.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/G0F5t66F6CxC830xLii032i3kfb6X6.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	20世紀的中國人是一種悲哀\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	他們的願望是：來生不是中國人！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/Qb8y7407BWeV4w4d45v04ZD77vd4W7.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/Qb8y7407BWeV4w4d45v04ZD77vd4W7.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	心裡你們在怎麼想\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/vt3EvlIp0V6P3vDLmL03303MZ3UuLP.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/vt3EvlIp0V6P3vDLmL03303MZ3UuLP.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	只有拿中國軍官的頭能換錢\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/C67bBx6WemeA6xD9DbyrKaDa9Xme72.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/C67bBx6WemeA6xD9DbyrKaDa9Xme72.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	朋友，别哭\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/a0Xv53Jd6VpjPlVVJdGWl5XpjV4NP6.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/a0Xv53Jd6VpjPlVVJdGWl5XpjV4NP6.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	人頭展示1\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/KgslzFF8fqSSSspiNNlPNgit08I98z.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/KgslzFF8fqSSSspiNNlPNgit08I98z.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	人頭展示2只恨我是中國人\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/QR86ofn9LTZ9rO9LGJj6nZPhINjOOh.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/QR86ofn9LTZ9rO9LGJj6nZPhINjOOh.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	特寫\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/qAa6Uw2DUy5AWAyUNNYayU66rUjE7M.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/qAa6Uw2DUy5AWAyUNNYayU66rUjE7M.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	下面那不是土，全是人\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/CWxsNTkxFkS5zXzWNbWAFBeen5SWF6.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/CWxsNTkxFkS5zXzWNbWAFBeen5SWF6.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	當殺人成為習慣\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/JCxdvhx74Ydsj4Vk7ZUHd9k4P4Wu0y.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/JCxdvhx74Ydsj4Vk7ZUHd9k4P4Wu0y.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:monospace;text-align:justify;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#021EAA;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">731细菌部队认罪录音：</span></strong></span>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<iframe class=\"video_iframe\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=o05370v73gy\">\r\n	</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<pre>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>惨绝人寰人体试验……</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1931年9月18日本在中国东北爆发的一次军事冲突和政治事件。冲突双方是中国东北军和日本关东军。根据冲突爆发的日期，史称“九·一八事变”。由于当时中国东北地区称为满洲，因此日本方面将这次事变称为“满洲事变”。 </span></strong> 这次事件爆发后的几年时间内，东北三省全部被日本关东军占领，因此被中国民众视为国耻，直至今日，9月18日在中国许多非正式场合都被称为“国耻日”。 <span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#0070C0;\"> 大家转发起来 ！！看过的中国人都已经转了  你还在犹豫什么 ！！勿忘国耻！转起来！ </span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n</pre>', '2017-10-04 10:40:45');
