span>将来容易畏首畏尾。</span></strong></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\">怜悯中长大的孩子<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\">，</span>将来容易自怨自艾。</span></strong></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\">嘲讽中长大的孩子<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\">，</span>将来容易消极退缩。</span></strong></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\">嫉妒中长大的孩子<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\">，</span>将来容易钩心斗角。</span></strong></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\">羞辱中长大的孩子<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\">，</span>将来容易心怀内疚。</span></strong></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\">容忍中长大的孩子<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\">，</span>将来必能极富耐性。</span></strong></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:20px;\">孩子是父母的镜子，父母是孩子的榜样。</span></strong></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:20px;color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\">\r\n			说的太对了！\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:20px;color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\">\r\n			传出去，不要私存！\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img width=\"384\" src=\"http://img.8htq.com.cn/upload/20161015/image80/147651322880.jpg?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" height=\"469\" style=\"width:384px;height:469px;\" /><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"line-height:22px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#0052FF;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5em;color:#002060;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5em;color:#00B0F0;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5em;color:#205867;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5em;color:#E36C09;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:20px;\"><img width=\"345\" src=\"http://img.8htq.com.cn/upload/20161026/image80/147745566180.png?tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" height=\"128\" style=\"width:345px;height:128px;\" /></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<h2 class=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:#3E3E3E;text-align:justify;font-family:宋体;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">舆论压力，平台常被封，如需查看更多“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.44px;color:#021EAA;\">爆料贪官污吏，欺行霸市，电视不敢曝光的丑闻；南海实时焦点，政治风云，更有正能量弘扬</span><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">\"的内幕消息请<span style=\"line-height:25.6px;color:#FFFB00;background-color:#000000;\">长按下方二维码</span>识别关注！！！</span></span></strong>\r\n	</h2>\r\n	<p style=\"font-fami