trong>1938年1月，毛泽东在延安会见来访的梁漱溟。</strong></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<br />\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<img src=\"http://image101.360doc.com/DownloadImg/2016/11/1119/84352709_18\" /> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<span style=\"font-family:inherit;\"><strong>1942年3月9日，毛泽东为中央职工委员会副书记张浩执绋。</strong></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<br />\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<img src=\"http://image101.360doc.com/DownloadImg/2016/11/1119/84352709_19\" /> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<strong>真的不能与老美比个头</strong> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<br />\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<img src=\"http://image101.360doc.com/DownloadImg/2016/11/1119/84352709_20\" /> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<span style=\"font-family:inherit;\"><strong>1942年5月，中共中央召开延安文艺座谈会，这是毛泽东、朱德等与参加延安文艺座谈会的代表们合影。</strong></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<img src=\"http://image101.360doc.com/DownloadImg/2016/11/1119/84352709_21\" /> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<span style=\"font-family:inherit;\"><strong>毛泽东在讲话，注意到主席的格子衬衫没</strong></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<br />\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<img src=\"http://image101.360doc.com/DownloadImg/2016/11/1119/84352709_22\" /> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<span style=\"font-family:inherit;\"><strong>吴莉莉（右）和毛泽东、朱德</strong></span> \r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<br />\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:inherit;\">\r\n							<img src=\"http://image101.360doc.com