r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/fVSDvVgLZm8VvVG3vVlSOG21G82Al2.gif\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"姐妹帮.gif\" />\r\n</p>', '2017-10-04 20:01:08');
INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('95', '<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://weiqin.xingchen123.top/attachment/images/2/2017/09/BW6mO6K5QZ5NEj8042Q5652V052mq5.gif\" width=\"100%\" class=\"weixin\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">今年张柏芝和谢霆锋的第二个儿子Quintus7岁了，继承了爸爸妈妈的高颜值，出落得非常可爱。<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/CFvLk3pTi2A4toQZ5AaWSWwwMAQwK4.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/CFvLk3pTi2A4toQZ5AaWSWwwMAQwK4.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">为了给Quintus庆祝生日，谢霆锋和父亲谢贤母亲狄波拉还有一堆亲友重现了家庭版的“峰味”，跟其他明星家庭举办豪华庆祝party不一样，谢霆锋为儿子办了一个很温馨的小型家庭生日聚会。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/sg4ZKeg6EgxkQyT4eVxteWLQe42eEX.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"1506226990(1).jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">张柏芝这边，也是11日工作结束后就马上赶往机场，行色匆匆，着急为儿子庆生。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/WFOEPTSAv5EW4kPSKApqx55W4OdzA1.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/WFOEPTSAv5EW4kPSKApqx55W4OdzA1.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/DHec5p54b2bEeApFEX4C445H4B2ha6.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/DHec5p54b2bEeApFEX4C445H4B2ha6.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">生日party也非常有爱。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/qELz1Etei8vZxI8sI9yTEAzzXXw781.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/qELz1Etei8vZxI8sI9yTEAzzXXw781.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/tsi55HOIFX4LOo9f9VGwFGiExxOi9N.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/tsi55HOIFX4LOo9f9VGwFGiExxOi9N.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">这些年，张柏芝一直陪伴着两个孩子长大，她对孩子的爱意，不用多说都只觉得快溢出荧幕。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/N4Vr1MAqEEmjZLZE5eVa1Lv5411oPT.gif\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/N4Vr1MAqEEmjZLZE5eVa1Lv5411oPT.gif\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/V62cMGTglsM6bxcSbtTGSSM6C9Mz2c.gif\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/V62cMGTglsM6bxcSbtTGSSM6C9Mz2c.gif\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">张柏芝演的第一部作品<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#FF4F79;\">《喜剧之王》</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/VSd1hLyYLUUydQDC9acQCIVuYvDA7k.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/VSd1hLyYLUUydQDC9acQCIVuYvDA7k.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">当小有名气的她开始陷入</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">和谢霆锋、王菲的三角恋之中，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">那年很多人都在骂她是小三！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/FAfeeCKUa32QkMnMg2e82q5U2eGc35.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/FAfeeCKUa32QkMnMg2e82q5U2eGc35.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">可也有很多人说她和谢霆锋才最配，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">爱情要对比， 才能知道和谁是真爱！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/kl982vk0optE89NzmUz870vl2p4Mo8.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/kl982vk0optE89NzmUz870vl2p4Mo8.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">后来，他们有了两个孩子，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">所有人都以为两个人会一直走下去。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">突然，艳照门事件如轰炸一般发生了，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她的幸福也从此不见了……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/HwSSaaLpFRlEZ4wN15ZaZtUUBSwuU4.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/HwSSaaLpFRlEZ4wN15ZaZtUUBSwuU4.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">经过艳照门事件后，他们离婚了！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她带着两个儿子独自生活，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她说，那个时候想过轻生，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">可是为了孩子硬是强撑着！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">这之后，为了挽救自己的声誉，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她开始拼命工作、演戏、努力生活~</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">直到现在我们看到了一个完美妈妈张柏芝！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/pbvUXaumz1gB8Uig1zsD86IPrxBjaS.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/pbvUXaumz1gB8Uig1zsD86IPrxBjaS.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/xvSILQqKZ9l9rQLjqbiTSbkm6IJQ24.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/xvSILQqKZ9l9rQLjqbiTSbkm6IJQ24.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">港媒曝出前段时间她和一男子的亲密照，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">大儿子抱着他的肩膀，可见关系亲密。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">更有媒体爆料，她已经准备二婚了！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/JfTpQbztUVTZU8F7BPuB8pB8Tfp73a.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/JfTpQbztUVTZU8F7BPuB8pB8Tfp73a.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">不知道这段消息的真实性，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">刚离婚没多久，谢霆锋就和王菲复合了。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">媒体问她怎么评论，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她说：真的假的……祝福呗……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">可以看出她并没有放下这段感情，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">给出的祝福也是那么不由衷！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/IpcqTXcI2oQp4Zzz1wPqp1ctPq11kK.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/IpcqTXcI2oQp4Zzz1wPqp1ctPq11kK.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">前段时间，更是让儿子录了视频，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">祝福锋菲恋！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/K8eE4c447ZjXDNH8HN9a7E23A83JnD.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/K8eE4c447ZjXDNH8HN9a7E23A83JnD.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">这时，一些媒体见不得娱乐圈风平浪静，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">硬是说张柏芝为了名气，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">永远都要拉着谢霆锋和王菲。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">私下她威胁谢霆锋不能再婚，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">甚至还有说她要和谢霆锋复婚</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/V7VS7w401190994PHzgPO4Hh1157gW.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/V7VS7w401190994PHzgPO4Hh1157gW.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">如今，两家人各自安好，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">就是再好不过的情况了，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">可还会有很多人在说她是戏精，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">不停的消费着前夫和儿子，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">力求维护一个好妈妈的人设！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">上越来越多的节目，晒很多照片都是在炒作，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/xZBF8f4FMf6zyvl466f575yL5nf67n.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/xZBF8f4FMf6zyvl466f575yL5nf67n.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她炒没炒作我不知道，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">但我知道她一直都是个好妈妈，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">曾经孩子很小，都是她抱在手里。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">连谢霆锋都说：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">我抱孩子半个小时就受不了了，<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">但是她能抱一整天不换手！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/e3Eedxv1ex5828UAytzzEw5d5uikA3.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/e3Eedxv1ex5828UAytzzEw5d5uikA3.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/aKJLTwfL2OfbmwLqLvllqVV2jK1L3n.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/aKJLTwfL2OfbmwLqLvllqVV2jK1L3n.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">就算是炒作，她没有炒作恋情，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">却一直选择和孩子们在一起，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">也是种良心炒作！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">但我始终不相信这是炒作，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">因为很多网友拍到为了照顾儿子，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她自己累倒了！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/Vgg4WlB4OGN44TIdHb4noan8iaifGD.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/Vgg4WlB4OGN44TIdHb4noan8iaifGD.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">为了让儿子多睡一会儿，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">她抱着儿子走了一路！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/R1XmWsSpnQZsqD4dqxZPqq4nWX4p1h.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/R1XmWsSpnQZsqD4dqxZPqq4nWX4p1h.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">30多度的高温天里，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">大儿子身体不舒服，瘦弱的她就背着走！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/OoDD6edrKZ7KddEN7RNGGFezEDrEki.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/OoDD6edrKZ7KddEN7RNGGFezEDrEki.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">看着她和儿子的合照，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">满满的都是爱！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">就连谢霆锋的爸爸都说：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">柏芝这个妈妈绝对合格！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">不要再盯着他们不放了，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">就让她和儿子们幸福的生活吧，<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">多一点宽容好吗？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:#3E3E3E;text-align:justify;font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">舆论压力，平台常被封，如需查看更多“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.44px;color:#021EAA;\">爆料贪官污吏，欺行霸市，电视不敢曝光的丑闻；南海实时焦点，政治风云，更有正能量弘扬</span><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">\"的内幕消息请<span style=\"line-height:25.6px;color:#FFFB00;background-color:#000000;\">长按下方二维码</span>识别关注！！！</span></span></strong>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/VP3DziijZJNwhHHwe3nbWIdIJ3ljhN.gif\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"姐妹帮.gif\" />\r\n</p>', '2017-10-04 20:02:37');
