an style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">还有多少时间够你把烦恼添；</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">时光匆匆又一年，</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">还有多少时日把笑容展</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/xJ88S86ZhcJ3F84F3t8n3C4jccY84H.png\" width=\"275\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/xJ88S86ZhcJ3F84F3t8n3C4jccY84H.png\" height=\"191\" style=\"width:275px;height:191px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">只要你活着，</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">就有累，有烦，有苦，有甜。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">与其多心，不如少根筋。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">人生一世，糊涂难得，难得糊涂。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">人这辈子，</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#974806;font-size:20px;\">有钱也好，没钱也罢，</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:1