体;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">舆论压力，平台常被封，如需查看更多“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.44px;color:#021EAA;\">爆料贪官污吏，欺行霸市，电视不敢曝光的丑闻；南海实时焦点，政治风云，更有正能量弘扬</span><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">\"的内幕消息请<span style=\"line-height:25.6px;color:#FFFB00;background-color:#000000;\">长按下方二维码</span>识别关注！！！</span></span></strong>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/Ke2OollV1LvWuyHbMkMZTGMHr2eWGm.gif\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/Ke2OollV1LvWuyHbMkMZTGMHr2eWGm.gif\" />\r\n</p>', '2017-10-04 21:46:01');
INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('136', '<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jgQmIsROGyoiNtiqZwqwvw\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/MNU5NtNtKuEwq5TztV1twN2ytz1CgT.gif\" width=\"100%\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jgQmIsROGyoiNtiqZwqwvw\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/U7nxzseRZ168khhn8NekZe6XM6MmW6.gif\" width=\"100%\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jgQmIsROGyoiNtiqZwqwvw\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/b2mo4FmMaYf2e4z7QeZ840M4JCZLYY.gif\" width=\"100%\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;color:#D00505;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#D92142;\"><strong>老毕下台，跟下面这些息息相关，很多人竟还天天这样做，</strong></span><strong>2017，<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">这十三件事千万别做了！</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;</span><strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">1.不要评价别人的好坏，因为他们并不影响你吃饭。</span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;color:#D00505;\">\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;2.不要评价别人的德行，因为你不见得比他更高尚。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3.不要评价别人的家庭，因为那和你没有一点关系</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;4.不要评价别人的学问，因为世上最不缺的就是学问。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">5.不要评价任何人，哪怕是你最看不起的人。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;6.不要胡乱花钱，因为明天你就可能失业。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;7.不要趾高气扬，因为明天你就可能失势。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">8.不要太过张扬，要明白没有一个人会比你更弱小。总之，做人要低调一点。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">9.不要滥交朋友，尤其是同性，因为一举一动都会留下烙印，将来成为是非。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">10.不要依靠别人，因为生活沉重，谁都想活得轻松。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\">&emsp;&emsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">11.不要伤害别人，因为报复迟早都会来，弄不好吃亏的是你自己。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;color:#002060;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;12.做人不要解释，是智者的选择。人生在世，我们常常产生想解释点什么的想法。然而，一旦解释起来，却发现任何人解释都是那样的苍白无力，甚至还会越抹越黑。</span></span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#002060;\">山不解释自己的高度，并不影响它耸立云端；海不解释自己的深度，并不影响它容纳百川；地不解释自己的厚度，但没有谁能取代她作为承载万物的地位……。</span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#002060;\">别低估任何人，你没那么多观众，别那么累。</span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;color:#D00505;\">\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;background-color:#92D050;\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#938953;background-color:#FAFAF0;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:宋体;color:#002060;\">13.不要随意发脾气，谁都不欠你的。现在很痛苦，等过阵子回头看看会发现其实那都不算事。我们常常抱怨生活对我们不公平，其实生活根本不知道我们是谁…</span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;color:#D00505;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;\">\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:medium;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#595959;background-color:#FFFFF0;\">\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;color:#D00505;\">\r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;color:#D00505;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong><span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">都说祸从口出，</span><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-size:24px;\">现在的人嘴碎到什么地步：</span></strong></span></strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>坐个别人车 ，就是小三了；</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>从宾馆出来的，就是和别人开房了；</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>和异性吃饭，关系就有一腿了；</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>出门超过半个月，就是外面有人了；</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>穿着洋气，就是不正经了；</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>没让你占便宜，就是装纯了；</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>还有就是上网聊天就是处老铁了；</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>尼玛这要是去殡仪馆参加个葬礼，出来就是鬼了，咋不吓死你呢？</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<strong>------送给那些嘴欠的人 !<strong><span>&nbsp;</span></strong><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:18px;text-align:center;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;\">最后再送你一段话！</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">不要弄丢，一个对你好的人；</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#002060;\">不要漠视，一份待你深的情。</span></strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">不是谁都能包容你的臭脾气，</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">更不是谁都能一直等下去</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"><br />\r\n没有什么比时间更值钱，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">也没有什么比感情更珍贵。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">一个人愿意陪着你，这就是爱你。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">找你聊天不是寂寞，而是担心你孤单；</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"><br />\r\n哄你开心不是没事做，而是怕你伤心。<br />\r\n珍惜一个对你好的人，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#002060;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#002060;\">因为：</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">失去了不再回来，错过了难再拥有！</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">真心如镜，碎了难圆；</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">真情似水，凉了难续。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">真正想念你的人，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">无论你在不在线，都会给你留言;</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#002060;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;font-family:Simsun;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">真正关心你的人，</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">看的不是空间，而是你的世界;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#002060;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">真正疼爱你的人，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"></span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">读的不是文字，而是你的心情。</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;font-family:Simsun;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\">真正心里有你的人，无所谓距离，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#002060;\"><br />\r\n无所谓时空，牵挂一直不变！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></strong></span>\r\n	</