INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('181', '<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://weiqin.xingchen123.top/attachment/images/2/2017/09/BW6mO6K5QZ5NEj8042Q5652V052mq5.gif\" width=\"100%\" class=\"weixin\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	9月23日，李湘和王岳伦的女儿王诗龄在微博上晒出一个她用英文示范解数学题的视频，并写道：<span style=\"color:#C00000;\"><strong>“周末在家写数学作业！”</strong></span>视频中，王诗龄用一口流利的英文解答18+9的方法，让不少网友赞叹。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/HkKCNkFkb2fVqAVKykQPVHkyapAQea.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/HkKCNkFkb2fVqAVKykQPVHkyapAQea.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	网友纷纷留言：<span style=\"color:#C00000;\"><strong>“这个英语发音让人服气！”“我的妈，七八岁的英文水平顶我读了十几年的英语。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/y3MgdaGszYqYnSCMGzYUgphz6MBMbu.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/y3MgdaGszYqYnSCMGzYUgphz6MBMbu.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	来看下8岁的王诗龄如何用一口流利的英语解数学题：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<iframe class=\"video_iframe\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=q0553xj0o4u\">\r\n	</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	不过看完视频，有网友表示，<span style=\"color:#C00000;\"><strong>计算18+9，她这方法愣是没看懂啊！</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/QyZRSuu2sRGnzI9PCpz99zXi2RgIyY.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/QyZRSuu2sRGnzI9PCpz99zXi2RgIyY.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	来看看Angela是怎么计算的……\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	首先，画一条数轴线，然后在上面画两个个圆弧；\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	然后，把9拆成5和4；\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	接着，先数18+5，19、20、21、22、23！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	最后，再数23+4，24、25、26、27！Bingo！答案出来了！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	之所以把9拆成5和4，大概是因为一只手只有5根手指吧……\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/GaC8o56qPG82O6p68GZ69z2fs2pso4.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/GaC8o56qPG82O6p68GZ69z2fs2pso4.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	热心网友给出更方便的算法……\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/x1ktZjY604Ym1y24rvJMr4yM11yV0k.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/x1ktZjY604Ym1y24rvJMr4yM11yV0k.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	不过话说回来，王诗龄的英语口语真不是盖的……<span>前段时间王诗龄一段秀英语的小视频也</span><span>在网上疯传。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<iframe class=\"video_iframe\" height=\"270\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=s0524c6ylaf\">\r\n	</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	据悉王诗龄就读的北京某国际学校，幼儿园、小学、初中、高中一体化，全英文教学，学费高达20万/年，招生十分严格，众多明星子女都曾在该校入读。华谊老总王中磊的儿子威廉、田亮的女儿森碟都是王诗龄的校友。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#3E3E3E;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://my6.mogudao.cn/attachment/images/3/2017/09/L83T338Ef9984802n2F9a2AnVZDv42.jpg\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"images/3/2017/09/L83T338Ef9984802n2F9a2AnVZDv42.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:#3E3E3E;text-align:center;font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size