441_543.png\" title=\"20171007133441_543.png\" alt=\"20171007133441_543.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007133459_335.png\" title=\"20171007133459_335.png\" alt=\"20171007133459_335.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007133534_653.png\" title=\"20171007133534_653.png\" alt=\"20171007133534_653.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NDk0NTE2NQ==&amp;mid=2247483652&amp;idx=5&amp;sn=c7eb0d6bd36030779d1dc880c9f5802a&amp;chksm=e9575966de20d070048a7da6ecf5b7ac5ce58d465347f2ed57a4ef7b0595fdf03e748b9e4d5d&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=25&amp;srcid=0820uSkVlBtgSJbWFgwJrkZ4&amp;pass_ticket=ISkrACBH%2BWRxdYsNkMbIRRnupKa5Uta09nauwikIuV%2By9jRa1VX9GoVdmYqa4Ox8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color:#176EBA;font-size:20px;\">生态环境大变样</span></strong></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NDk0NTE2NQ==&amp;mid=2247483652&amp;idx=5&amp;sn=c7eb0d6bd36030779d1dc880c9f5802a&amp;chksm=e9575966de20d070048a7da6ecf5b7ac5ce58d465347f2ed57a4ef7b0595fdf03e748b9e4d5d&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=25&amp;srcid=0820uSkVlBtgSJbWFgwJrkZ4&amp;pass_ticket=ISkrACBH%2BWRxdYsNkMbIRRnupKa5Uta09nauwikIuV%2By9jRa1VX9GoVdmYqa4Ox8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color:#176EBA;line-height:25.6px;\"></span></strong></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007133826_916.png\" title=\"20171007133826_916.png\" alt=\"20171007133826_916.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007133827_591.png\" title=\"20171007133827_591.png\" alt=\"20171007133827_591.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007133827_188.png\" title=\"20171007133827_188.png\" alt=\"20171007133827_188.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007133849_771.png\" title=\"20171007133849_771.png\" alt=\"20171007133849_771.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	以前有人说，中国人没有信仰。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	但是，看完这个纪录片，我发现中国人其实是有信仰的，这个信仰被深深的刻在骨子里，100多年了，从来不敢忘记，始终砥砺前行。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007134553_713.png\" title=\"20171007134553_713.png\" alt=\"20171007134553_713.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007134604_173.gif\" title=\"20171007134604_173.gif\" alt=\"20171007134604_173.gif\" />\r\n</p>', '2017-10-07 13:46:21');
INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('215', '<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135459_617.gif\" title=\"20171007135459_617.gif\" alt=\"20171007135459_617.gif\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span>自从海湾战争爆发后，美军几乎打了一场教科书般的现代化战争。在这场战争中，100多万的伊拉克军队，几乎被吊锤，毫无还手之力。在这场战争中，美国通过太空中的卫星，牢牢地占据了信息和通讯的制高点。并且，在“沙漠风暴”行动中，投掷了大量的精确制导炸弹，还首次实战使用了“战斧”巡航导弹。从数百公里之外发射，精准地命中目标，命中率达到100%。可以说，太空中的美国卫星起到了至关重要的作用。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135540_123.png\" title=\"20171007135540_123.png\" alt=\"20171007135540_123.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\">美国“战斧”巡航导弹<br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span>而海湾战争，也一战震惊了世界，改变了战争的规则。那个以人数优势弥补装备劣势的时代已经一去不复返了，高科技的精英军队，才是制胜的法宝。那时，中国的卫星技术虽谈不上国际顶尖，但也在老一辈科学家们的努力下，奠定了根基。中国拥有着一批年轻的卫星科研骨干人才。而后，在中国经济快速发展的背景下，不缺钱的卫星事业也迎来了稳步高速发展。如今在建的北斗导航系统，更是打破美国GPS系统的垄断地位，将成为比GPS更为先进的全球导弹定位系统。目前，北斗系统已经在中国航海和共享单车中大量商用。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135554_683.png\" title=\"20171007135554_683.png\" alt=\"20171007135554_683.png\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span>但，在今年的7月2日，中国发射了一颗由长征五号搭载的“实践18号”卫星，因火箭故障而发射失败，“实践18号”卫星也因此坠海。在人类卫星发射试验中，这不过只是一次平常的失败任务，但却引发了世界的关注。国内外普通群众除了为中国卫星发射失败而感到吃惊之外，大多数是从科学的角度，为中国航天加油鼓劲。但部分国家的军方，则对坠海的实践18号卫星更有兴趣。各国纷纷出动了大批的海军舰艇，进行紧急争抢性地打捞！其中，美国海军最为积极！</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135606_558.png\" title=\"20171007135606_558.png\" alt=\"20171007135606_558.png\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\">长征五号运载火箭发射失败<br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span>这是为什么呢？小编记得，当长征五号发射失败后，主流媒体的目光，基本都锁定在长征五号的故障之上，极少有提到“实践18号”卫星。大家有所不知的是，“实践18号”发射失败后，坠入了西太平洋，靠近澳大利亚海域。美国海军军舰当即前往坠落海域进行抢先打捞，随后，诸多国家也参与其中。这些国家可不是为了帮助中国，他们无一不是觊觎“实践18号”卫星的技术！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135616_186.png\" title=\"20171007135616_186.png\" alt=\"20171007135616_186.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span>众所周知，“墨子号”量子卫星是中国发射的，全球第一颗量子通信卫星。而“实践18号”则是继“墨子号”之后，中国准备发射的第二颗量子通信验证卫星，其上所包含的是中国研制的，全球最为先进的量子通信技术！关于量子通信技术，中国处于全球领跑地位，即便是美国，也跟不上中国的脚步。如今，“实践18号”卫星坠入海中，对于美国等国家而言，即便是残骸，那也具有着巨大的价值啊！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135626_685.png\" title=\"20171007135626_685.png\" alt=\"20171007135626_685.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span>从这里，我们也可以看到美国的丑陋面目。一面对中国实行技术封禁，另一面却想着窃取中国的量子卫星技术。从反面来看，也表明中国正在局部性对美国实现技术反超。“墨子”号量子卫星于2016年8月发射，如今已经过去了一年，而其他国家却没有任何动作。这说明，中国正在量子通信领域拉开与其他国家的差距。这也可看出，量子通信卫星技术绝非轻易能够研制成功。美国这么急不可耐，可见其已经狗急跳墙。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135636_514.png\" title=\"20171007135636_514.png\" alt=\"20171007135636_514.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span>不过，中国也无需担心，通常来说，卫星上都安装了自毁系统。一旦出现发射失败，中国方面完全可以启动自会系统，对其进行销毁，以免核心技术泄露。反正，中国掌握着完整的设计资料，这次失败，还可以再造重来。而美国即便打捞到一些残骸，也最多窃取一些边缘技术，难以窥探到“实践18号”卫星的量子核心通信技术！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135658_753.png\" title=\"20171007135658_753.png\" alt=\"20171007135658_753.png\" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007135729_410.gif\" title=\"20171007135729_410.gif\" alt=\"20171007135729_410.gif\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>', '2017-10-07 16:13:29');
INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('216', '<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007140335_631.gif\" title=\"20171007140335_631.gif\" alt=\"20171007140335_631.gif\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007140914_536.png\" title=\"20171007140914_536.png\" alt=\"20171007140914_536.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">国人体质逐年下降已是不争的事实。我们周围童年患白血病的，少年得癌的，学生体测猝死的，青年、中年过劳死的新闻，已经不再是新闻。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">江浙某处8成儿童体内兽用抗生素超标，某地8成公务员身体亚健康……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">我在评论中认为，饮食垃圾化是体质下降的主要原因，而缺乏合适的锻炼，也是诱发体质下降的重要因素。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong>缺乏体质锻炼，不是因为国人懒，而是各个年龄层次的人把日子都过错了。</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007140925_479.png\" title=\"20171007140925_479.png\" alt=\"20171007140925_479.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">人的孩提时代，应该怎么过？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">应该是以玩为主，通过玩游戏来认识世界，锻炼体质意志，从而为今后的学习打下兴趣和身体的好底子。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">但我们的孩子，现在在幼年时期都在干什么？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">小小年纪就在玩命地学习。一句极具煽动性的口号，把全国的儿童都推进了深渊，那就是：绝不能让孩子输在起跑线上！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">于是，你家孩子两岁学唐诗，我家必然一岁就学，你家孩子一岁学外语，我家孩子胎教就学外语！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">总之，恨不能把孩子的起跑线划到妈妈的肚子里。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">一个两三岁的孩子，又是画画，又是弹钢琴，凡是天下的知识，恨不得三岁前全部灌到孩子的肚子里。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">孩子在玩的过程中锻炼的机会和天性被生生剥夺，太多的孩子还没上学，就已经戴上了眼镜。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong>谁都知道这不对，但谁都不会带头纠正。因为变态的社会竞争必然带来变态的被动适应，人人觉得危机，便人人不能自拔。</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007141003_805.png\" title=\"20171007141003_805.png\" alt=\"20171007141003_805.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">再看看青年人都在干什么？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">青春期本来是用来学习的最好时光，可今天的年轻人，都在拼命的玩手机、玩游戏。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong>正所谓玩物丧志，玩垮了意志，玩毁了青春，也玩坏了体质。</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">这里也有一句迷惑人的口号，叫“我的青春我做主”。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">我的儿子，考取的是国内一流的大学，可自从进入大学校园之后，就完全沉溺于网络游戏，四年大学，居然只去过两次校内图书馆。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">每天晚上，上网玩到深夜两点不睡觉，白天经常因为起不了床而逃课。每门功课基本都是60分万岁。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">可怕的是，今天的大学里，基本都是这样。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">刚刚走上社会的青年人，为了扩大人脉，适应黑色竞争，争相出入吃喝场所，动不动喝得烂醉如泥，长身体长智慧的年龄，却被活生生地糟蹋掉了。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">中年人能顾及一点身体的健康吗？更不能了。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">因为上有老要孝敬，下有小要培养，一个家要经营，一套房子的贷款要月供。职场打拼从来就是没有人性可言的，除了拼命赚钱，还能有什么别的奢望？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007141017_715.png\" title=\"20171007141017_715.png\" alt=\"20171007141017_715.png\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">我们冷静地看看，也只有老年人因为感觉自己的身体一天不如一天，为了能在这个世上多看几眼，才开始拼命地健身！那帮跳广场舞的老头老太，才是把身体当回事的人。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong>孩子们该玩，却在拼命地学习；</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong>青年人该学习，却在拼命地游戏；</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong>中年人该顾惜身体，却在拼命赚钱；</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong>老年人该颐养天年，却开始拼命地健身。</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">中国人从小到大，全把日子过错了，过反了，这不仅是每个社会成员的悲哀，更是这个社会的悲哀。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\">究竟在哪个环节出了问题，我想，该有人出来说说了。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007141053_361.png\" title=\"20171007141053_361.png\" alt=\"20171007141053_361.png\" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:14px;color:#A1A1A1;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007141101_979.gif\" title=\"20171007141101_979.gif\" alt=\"20171007141101_979.gif\" /><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>', '2017-10-07 14:11:23');
INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('217', '<h2 class=\"rich_media_title\" id=\"activity-name\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:24px;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <br />\r\n	</h2>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"http://weiqin.xingchen123.top/attachment/images/2/2017/09/BW6mO6K5QZ5NEj8042Q5652V052mq5.gif\" width=\"100%\" class=\"weixin\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong>最好的爱情是什么样的？</strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span><strong><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">有人说，最好的爱情</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">是提到TA的名字你就眉飞色舞</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">想到TA的样子你就春心荡漾</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">还有人说，最好的爱情</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">是骄傲的人低头，倔强的人服软</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">在鲸鱼看来，最好的爱情</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">就是哪怕世间万般好 </span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">他也只钟情于你</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">牵着你的手，从心动到古稀</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">且以白头共余生，从此情深到永恒</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;\">01</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">成都84岁的刘大爷载着老伴出门逛街，两个人有说有笑的模样，羡煞旁人。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007142752_179.jpg\" title=\"20171007142752_179.jpg\" alt=\"20171007142752_179.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">听说刘大爷骑的偏斗自行车，在上世纪80年代的成都，就已经成了载老婆出门的专用款。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007142815_846.jpg\" title=\"20171007142815_846.jpg\" alt=\"20171007142815_846.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">廖婆婆说，自打退休以后，老伴就买了这辆车。这车跟了他们几十年，刘大爷也载了婆婆几十年，<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong>“只要天气好就会带她逛逛”</strong></span>。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007142837_519.jpg\" title=\"20171007142837_519.jpg\" alt=\"20171007142837_519.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">最简单的浪漫，就是陪伴；最动听的誓言，就是一生只爱你一个人。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;\">02</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">有网友在地铁上，拍到了温暖人心的一幕：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">一位老奶奶的鞋子坏了，她的老伴不仅帮她修好，还细心地帮她穿上。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143021_552.jpg\" title=\"20171007143021_552.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143021_552.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老伴信心满满地对奶奶说：<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span>“不要担心，有我呢！”</span></strong></span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143033_457.jpg\" title=\"20171007143033_457.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143033_457.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">看，老奶奶笑得多甜呀！</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143045_223.jpg\" title=\"20171007143045_223.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143045_223.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">幸福就是我需要你时，而你恰好就在我身边&nbsp;，哪怕已经白发苍苍！</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;\">03</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">一位老奶奶在给她的老伴儿拍照，爷爷坐在布朗熊旁边，嘴角荡漾着孩童般的笑容。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143057_262.jpg\" title=\"20171007143057_262.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143057_262.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">爷爷腿脚不便，只能走短距离的路。拍完照，奶奶慢慢地推着爷爷走远了。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143109_765.jpg\" title=\"20171007143109_765.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143109_765.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">无论沧海桑田，身旁总有人懂你的低头不语，小心翼翼守护着你的孩子气，这大概就是爱情最好的模样了吧？</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">04</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">前几天，一封61岁老伯的辞职信火遍网络，引发网友纷纷感慨：</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#9A1212;\">“<strong>这才是真正嫁对了人啊！</strong>”</span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143120_375.jpg\" title=\"20171007143120_375.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143120_375.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">辞职信里是这样写的：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#888888;\">我要带老婆去贝加尔湖拍婚纱，这是她一直的心愿。到了我这个年纪就会明白，老婆才是最重要的。</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">对我来说，重要的事情只剩下三件，如果要把它们从轻到重排列，我想应该是这样的：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">我爱你。</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">爱你。</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">你。</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#AB1942;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">05</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">今年88岁的吴爷爷和86岁的李奶奶自幼相识，青梅竹马，自从1954年结婚以来，60多年两人一直同伴同行，从未分开过，直到去年李奶奶因病住院。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143136_315.jpg\" title=\"20171007143136_315.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143136_315.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">吴爷爷因为腿脚不好无法常看望，于是坚持每天给老伴写信，在医院里，儿子拿着信，俯下身靠近母亲耳边，一字一句地读给她听。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">当儿子念到<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span>“你一脸笑值千金”</span></strong></span>的时候，母亲李河清的眼角有些湿润了。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143220_304.jpg\" title=\"20171007143220_304.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143220_304.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#888888;\">（吴爷爷写给老伴的信）</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">深情不及久伴，厚爱无需多言。因为我娶了你，所以才要更拼命地对你好。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#888888;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#888888;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">06</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">照片上的老爷爷叫王力金，96岁。奶奶叫黄邵珍，84岁。1951年，相差12岁的他们，在一次文艺活动中相识，而后结为夫妻。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143319_562.jpg\" title=\"20171007143319_562.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143319_562.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">相伴64年，王力金穿过的所有衣服，都是由黄邵珍亲手缝制的。有一次王力金开玩笑说：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#888888;font-size:15px;\">“你给我做了这么多的衣服啊？一年穿一件，说不定穿不完我就走咯！”</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">黄邵珍深情地握着他的手，笑道：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#9A1212;\"><strong>“老头子，你给我记住：穿不完，不许走！”</strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143330_580.jpg\" title=\"20171007143330_580.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143330_580.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老一辈的爱情，也许就是一句简单的承诺，没有盛大的婚礼，没有鲜花和跑车，但一针一线，都藏着浓浓的爱意。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">07</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">一家游戏厅里，大家都被一对夫妻吸引。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老爷爷正在专心地抓娃娃，老奶奶在一旁指挥着，手里拎满了爷爷今晚为她抓的礼物。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"> </span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">转头看到别人在围观，老奶奶晃了晃手里的玩偶，笑着说：“我老头很厉害的～”</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143544_179.jpg\" title=\"20171007143544_179.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143544_179.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">即使老了，我们的爱情也正年轻，陪你享受一如既往的浪漫。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">08</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#AB1942;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">长沙街头，一位乞讨的老爷爷，买了蛋糕给老伴过生日。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">奶奶看着手里的蛋糕，开心的像个孩子。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143554_532.jpg\" title=\"20171007143554_532.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143554_532.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">吃完蛋糕，两人互相搀扶着消失在茫茫夜色。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143608_549.jpg\" title=\"20171007143608_549.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143608_549.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">不管未来有多艰难，只要有你陪伴，即使白发苍苍，我也愿随你去流浪。<br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">09</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>爷爷和奶奶在玩游戏，奶奶使尽了洪荒之力，假牙都掉出来了。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>爷爷让着奶奶，只用了很小力。看到奶油拍到了爷爷脸上，奶奶害羞得如同少女一般。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>爷爷猝不及防地亲了奶奶一口，这狗粮我吃了！</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">以后还要一起疯闹，余生请你慢慢指教。</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">10</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">年轻时，奶奶是个大大咧咧的姑娘，走路经常不看路。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">于是只要出门过马路，爷爷就会牵起奶奶的手。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">没曾想，这一牵，便从年少牵到了暮夕。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143805_558.jpg\" title=\"20171007143805_558.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143805_558.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>我知道人潮拥挤，我知道未来风雨阴晴不定，但有你陪伴，就不会孤单。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">11</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">还记得老夏和脆鹅的故事吗？</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老夏患有阿尔兹海默症，什么事情眨眼就忘记，唯一没有忘记的是对脆鹅的爱。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老夏96岁生日那天，家里没有蛋糕，没有蜡烛，没有礼物，有的只是脆鹅深情一吻。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143825_936.jpg\" title=\"20171007143825_936.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143825_936.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">令人伤心的是，这位可爱的老爷爷前不久去世了。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">弥留之际，脆鹅扶着老夏的后脑勺说：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#888888;\">“乖乖的，你就放心，好好的走吼…”</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#888888;\">“不用担心，我会照顾好自己。”</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143836_736.jpg\" title=\"20171007143836_736.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143836_736.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">往后你不在的日子里，风雪是你，平淡是你，清贫是你，荣华是你，心底温柔是你，目光所至，都是你。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">12</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#AB1942;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>他今年90岁，她今年89岁，这是他们结婚65周年的纪念照。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>其实老奶奶患上阿兹海默症，几乎忘掉身边所有的人和事，而老爷爷是她唯一没有遗忘的人。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143847_159.jpg\" title=\"20171007143847_159.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143847_159.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>老来多健忘，唯不忘相思。遇到世上最好的你，我宁愿花光所有运气。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#AB1942;\">13</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>从来不羡慕街头拥吻的情侣，只羡慕像他们一样牵手过马路的老夫妻。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>一起买菜逛市场，还不忘买束她最爱的鲜花。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143857_308.jpg\" title=\"20171007143857_308.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143857_308.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>怦然心动只是刹那惊艳，柴米油盐才是一辈子的生活方式。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>好的感情，不是一下子就把你感动晕，而是细水长流地把你宠坏。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">14</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>国外一位爷爷生病住院，就在去世前的几天，他已经陷入昏迷，却一直拉着奶奶的手。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143910_552.jpg\" title=\"20171007143910_552.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143910_552.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>人生不易，这辈子谢谢你，愿意陪我风雨同舟；</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>下辈子，还要做你的枕边人。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">15</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">俄罗斯一个村庄，一对老夫妻结婚65周年，老爷爷决定拍一张合影留念。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">刚开始两个人比较拘谨 ，后来摄影师要求老爷爷放松，展现最自然的一面。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007143921_670.jpg\" title=\"20171007143921_670.jpg\" alt=\"20171007143921_670.jpg\" /></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老爷爷立刻抱着老奶奶的脸颊，送给她深情地一吻，老奶奶幸福地哈哈大笑。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144015_419.jpg\" title=\"20171007144015_419.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144015_419.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">美好的感情不仅是年少时，如花绽放般热烈。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">也要像海一样彼此包容，相伴到暮年。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">16</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">凌晨在台北的机场，一位老奶奶在大厅内乱转，好像在着急地找什么人。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">突然一个臂膀将她搂入怀中，嘴里还念叨着：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"color:#888888;font-size:15px;\">老太婆，不是让你站在原地等我吗？这么晚了，不要离我太远。以后迷路了你站着别动，我来接你。</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144028_788.jpg\" title=\"20171007144028_788.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144028_788.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">一个人爱你在乎你，就会忍不住紧张你，紧张你被别人伤害到，紧张不小心委屈了你。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">17</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">一对老两口买电影票，老奶奶嫌贵说不看了吧，老爷爷掏钱说：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">“其实我根本不爱看这玩意儿，是这个小妹妹想看。”</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span></strong></span><span style=\"color:#AB1942;\"><strong></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#AB1942;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144041_261.jpg\" title=\"20171007144041_261.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144041_261.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">就算时光催人老，你的脸上布满皱纹，他的头发花白不复盛年，就算岁月几多变迁，你依然是他最宠爱的小丫头。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">18</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">八十多岁的章奶奶，一个人到派出所补办身份证。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">因为需要把耳环摘下来拍照，民警想上前帮忙，章奶奶谢绝了好意，一个电话叫来了老伴张爷爷给她摘。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"> </span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">张爷爷果然不辞辛苦，以最快的速度赶来。民警事后问她为什么，她笑着说：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">“因为老头子给我摘了几十年了，换别人摘我怕疼啊！”</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144053_438.jpg\" title=\"20171007144053_438.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144053_438.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">一见钟情容易，相濡以沫太难。有的人说不上哪里好，但就是谁都替代不了。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">19</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">国外有对老顽童夫妇，老奶奶不愿洗碗。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老爷爷说：</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#888888;\">“我来洗吧，你去休息。”</span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">老奶奶说：</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#888888;\">“不，我陪你吧，你洗我收。”</span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">结果，老爷爷洗的过程中，老奶奶的左手一直放在爷爷的屁屁上。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144105_664.jpg\" title=\"20171007144105_664.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144105_664.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#000000;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">听说这个习惯，从结婚延续到现在。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">真正的爱情就是无需掩饰，就是我的世界只许你一人放肆。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:18px;background-color:#9A1212;\"><strong>20</strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>得知83岁的妻子即将出院回家，也许此生再无相见可能，91岁的林生华来到妻子病床前，希望再陪妻子最后一程，再好好看看她的模样。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144115_820.jpg\" title=\"20171007144115_820.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144115_820.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>病床上，两双布满褶皱的手紧紧握在一起，林生华的眼泪夺眶而出。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144126_374.jpg\" title=\"20171007144126_374.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144126_374.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">岁月如梭两鬓风，流年胭脂眉间红。&nbsp;再捋青丝浓雪染，不悔经年此相逢。</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">与君百岁，终需一别。</span></strong></span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#AB1942;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">纵使银发两鬓，容颜老去，在我眼里，你还是当初的模样。</span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">长辈们常说</span><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\">：</span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">“我们那个年代，什么东西坏了都会想要修，现在什么坏了都想着换。”</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, STHeiti;font-size:15px;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:15px;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#888888;\">那个年代，牵了手就是一辈子。</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#888888;\">那个年代，感情很纯粹，只要认定了就不后悔。</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:15px;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#888888;\">那个年代，车马邮件都很慢，一生只够爱一个人。</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171007144136_727.jpg\" title=\"20171007144136_727.jpg\" alt=\"20171007144136_727.jpg\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:15px;\">等我们老了，也许才会真的明白：</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">说再多的爱，都不如和你一起慢慢变老。</span></strong></span></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n一起从清晨到日暮，从心动到古稀。</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\">执子之手，与子偕老，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\">从天光乍破到暮雪白头。</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#9A1212;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#AB1942;font-size:15px;\"> </span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<h1 style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:Arial;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<p style=\"color:#494429;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:medium;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#D82821;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;line-height:22.39px;font-size:14px;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#D82821;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;line-height:22.39px;font-size:14px;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><strong><img width=\"319\" src=\"http://img.8htq.com.cn/upload/20160922/image33/147451297733.jpg?wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" height=\"68\" style=\"width:319px;height:68px;\" /><br />\r\n</strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span> </strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</h1>\r\n	<h2 class=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:#3E3E3E;text-align:center;font-family:宋体;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</h2>\r\n	<h2 class=\"\" style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:#3E3E3E;text-align:center;font-family:宋体;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">舆论压力，平台常被封，如需查看更多“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.44px;color:#021EAA;\">爆料贪官污吏，欺行霸市，电视不敢曝光的丑闻；南海实时焦点，政治风云，更有正能量弘扬</span><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">\"的内幕消息请<span style=\"line-height:25.6px;color:#FFFB00;background-color:#000000;\">长按下方二维码</span>识别关注！！！</span></span></strong> \r\n	</h2>\r\n	<p style=\"font-size:medium;text-align:center;color:#494429;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#D82821;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;line-height:22.39px;font-size:14px;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#D82821;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;line-height:22.39px;font-size:14px;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong>