INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('243', '<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091040_811.gif\" title=\"20171008091040_811.gif\" alt=\"20171008091040_811.gif\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#FFFB00;\"><strong>货车司机一生中有四碗面最难吃！往大了说就得到处找活拉活，往小了说，既要照顾好老婆孩子，又要照顾好年迈的父母。所以要想过得好，活得好，就必须将这四碗面吃的好！</strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091139_533.png\" title=\"20171008091139_533.png\" alt=\"20171008091139_533.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <strong><span style=\"color:#7B0C00;font-size:20px;background-color:#FFFB00;\">第一碗面：体面！</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	干卡车司机这一行，脏活累活干了不少；每天吃住都在车上，困了有时候还不能睡；货送到了，装卸工忙不过来的时候，卡友们也得跟着搬；轮胎或者车坏了，小毛病的话，就必须自己上手......\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091151_475.png\" title=\"20171008091151_475.png\" alt=\"20171008091151_475.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	很多卡友因此常常被搞得风尘仆仆，狼狈不堪，哪里还有什么体面可讲？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"color:#7B0C00;font-size:20px;background-color:#FFFB00;\"><strong>第二碗面：门面！</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	俗话说的好，“伸手不打笑面虎”，时常保持一张笑脸，哪怕是遭遇到货主的刁难，哪怕是遇到交警路政，面对微笑的你，也会手下留情！做好微笑这张门面，货源滚滚来！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091203_844.png\" title=\"20171008091203_844.png\" alt=\"20171008091203_844.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"color:#7B0C00;font-size:20px;background-color:#FFFB00;\"><strong>第三碗面：情面！</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	货车司机是最重情重义的人，他们充分发挥着一方有难，八方支援的精神。同车的兄弟都会互相照顾，路上碰到卡友也会互相帮助，在休息站也会轮流休息，防止油耗子偷油；他们将所有的货车人都当做家人般看待！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091213_710.png\" title=\"20171008091213_710.png\" alt=\"20171008091213_710.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	除此之外，货车司机对家人，对家里的亲戚也是十分尽心尽力，谁家盖房子需要拉砖、拉货，二话不说开着货车就去了；生活再苦再累他们都扛着，累了也从来不对老婆孩子发脾气，一个人将苦埋在心里，每次过节回家看老爹老娘手里提着的过节礼物总是所有亲戚中最丰厚的。\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091233_629.png\" title=\"20171008091233_629.png\" alt=\"20171008091233_629.png\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	他们从不言苦，每次觉得苦的时候，看看老婆孩子的笑脸，再苦都觉得值得了！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <span style=\"color:#7B0C00;font-size:20px;background-color:#FFFB00;\"><strong>第四碗面：泡面！</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	提起泡面，几乎每个货车司机都会闻之色变。跑车的这十几年，吃过的泡面都能堆成小山丘那么高，真的不想再吃了，可是却又不得不吃，因为饥饿的时候，泡面就是行车路上最美味的食物！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091245_148.png\" title=\"20171008091245_148.png\" alt=\"20171008091245_148.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;font-size:16px;color:#666666;font-family:sans-serif;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"> 所以现在你有两个选择：</span></strong></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:Arial;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:Arial;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;font-size:medium;color:#494429;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">1. 无视 ,</span></strong></span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;font-size:medium;color:#494429;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;\">2. 让更多人看到！引起重视！</span></strong></span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;font-size:medium;color:#494429;font-family:微软雅黑;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;\">我选择了让更多人看到，因为我不想冷漠！</span></strong></span></strong></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px;color:#666666;font-family:sans-serif;\">\r\n	<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><img width=\"345\" src=\"http://img.8htq.com.cn/upload/20160922/image36/147451297736.jpg?wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" height=\"82\" style=\"width:345px;height:82px;\" /></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong>\r\n	</div>\r\n<strong>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#D82821;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;line-height:22.39px;font-size:14px;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#D82821;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;line-height:22.39px;font-size:14px;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><strong><img width=\"345\" src=\"http://img.8htq.com.cn/upload/20160922/image33/147451297733.jpg?wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" height=\"75\" style=\"width:345px;height:75px;\" /></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong>\r\n	</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">舆论压力，平台常被封，如需查看更多“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.44px;color:#021EAA;\">爆料贪官污吏，欺行霸市，电视不敢曝光的丑闻；南海实时焦点，政治风云，更有正能量弘扬</span><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\">\"的内幕消息请<span style=\"line-height:25.6px;color:#FFFB00;background-color:#000000;\">长按下方二维码</span>识别关注！！！</span></span></strong> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091520_647.gif\" title=\"20171008091520_647.gif\" alt=\"20171008091520_647.gif\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:16px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n	</p>', '2017-10-08 09:57:59');
INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('244', '<img src=\"http://weiqin.xingchen123.top/attachment/images/2/2017/09/BW6mO6K5QZ5NEj8042Q5652V052mq5.gif\" width=\"100%\" class=\"weixin\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:inherit;line-height:inherit;\">\r\n<p>\r\n	10月6日，一则“两辆外地牌号的越野车在西藏追逐碾压藏羚羊”的消息在微信朋友圈广泛传播。有网友称，车辆在追逐过程中致数只藏羚羊死亡。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	6日下午，青海可可西里国家级自然保护区管理局回应称，事件发生在5日下午的保护区内，并未造成藏羚羊受伤或死亡。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	朋友圈的消息称，一辆XB.YH**和一辆XD. A5H**的越野车正在戈壁上追逐藏羚羊群。图片显示，两辆越野车一前一后行驶，十余头藏羚羊在其间奔跑，其中一辆越野车距离藏羚群还十分靠近。\r\n</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicI9Bq5rZu2FlhveicnQtzbzP3Qev7TEiaP4VHI4sIOqybtliaic2HBdRVz6A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicIIO0G1icVLcsOwsicnJRfktluwicgRZEKickyKALRyG1Fbzic6I7UY2iacsqQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:670px !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicIFbdhq7UkrZ3FAoJibtKuicRib3JlkNKLV7WKlofV6AneCxhPRMhbQo4qA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	有网友称，两辆越野车在追逐过程中致使数只藏羚羊死亡。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	另有网友在新浪微博上发布图片消息称，涉事的两辆越野车目前停留在拉萨洲际大饭店。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicIxYHyJrOTtjzhjAfYNQNuDicfdmvuzgc1lVmvndfiaesh7wibkNnOWRmqg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:670px !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicIXE78W17zHHQ1LewNZnhhUgNwhLG4TDLJr2w5z0bT2Yqgsfwp7e4Z1A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	网友看到消息后，都非常气愤。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicI1EMAwSPQDiaicK8eGbq71dTx86Ribq3Thd45AxP1mHTFovT0FdpJEnaLQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	甚至还有网友个人开出了<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\">悬赏5万</span></strong>的筹码，希望有人能提供这两人的行踪。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicICiaAucSlXTxuYjapcBLY77ibXSXMu8bE2tBm74y5V4JBo0LGQs8towKA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicICuExVu5qUoA1yJAjuW1xF4GazydjvZbQwxFuBUExPnCsDA6HnTo6sA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	6日下午，青海可可西里国家级自然保护区管理局值班室工作人员称，此事发生在5日下午保护区内公路两旁的试验区内。<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\">两辆越野车的行为很快被保护站的工作人员发现并制止。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\">据该工作人员介绍，越野车司机事后解释，看到藏羚羊群出于好奇便将车辆驶离公路进入试验区，以便更近距离观察。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\">该工作人员还表示，事件并未导致有藏羚羊死亡。</span></strong>事发后保护站已经对涉事司机进行了处理，但具体情况不便透露。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	青海可可西里国家级自然保护区的工作人员说处理了涉事司机，但与该说法不同的是，<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\">拉萨警方却说，他们还在调查处理中……</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicIL6eUEf8cA57meaTe6IvESuwBp5wLRWq6GEY5zCicgmgXbiaM8aKuTBZQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	现场网友也表示，拉萨警方已经赶往涉事司机所在的酒店，全力追捕这两名司机。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicIiaTRP1CJZhrXpsl3yxY3xYs3oicMX5yic96QG9988NBTYwWXIUP8T5CUw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	据这名网友介绍，这两位司机已经离开酒店，但警方已设立关卡予以堵截。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	拉萨警方的速度赢得了网友的一致好评：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/G8vkERUJibkul8jLg9J7602wOyApRlH3sU6L7vzAthYcYEGydFCice3gCLRX0dDCG1U7EyjNniboo3uroxxek4zkg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	历史纪录中，藏羚羊的数量曾达到百万只之多，但环境恶化、偷捕盗猎导致其数量急剧下降，1995年全西藏也只剩5万多只。但随着近年来国家对藏羚羊的保护力度逐渐加大，目前藏羚羊种群的数量不断恢复。2016年9月4日，世界自然保护联盟宣布，将藏羚羊的受威胁程度由濒危降为易危。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	国家和人民都在重视藏羚羊，你们还敢开车进藏羚羊保护区“近距离观察”？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	不过不要紧，<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\">现在你们知道被追逐的藏羚羊是什么滋味了，一个都别想跑！</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\"></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicI0Nkicia9OibtzeticamXWnwf9mOwfrZyRll4fwZwRDVFv8Il2z9oXBBL7w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:670px !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#021EAA;\">最新消息，</span></strong><span>10月6日</span><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;\">下午16时许，两辆车到拉萨后准备入住拉萨圣地天堂洲际大酒店，并卸掉车辆牌照将车辆藏匿在区水利厅附近。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.6;\">17时许，联合森林公安成功将两辆涉案车的7名乘员控制，并找到藏匿车辆。<span style=\"line-height:1.6;color:#021EAA;\"><strong>目前，警方正对7人进行调查审理。</strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wZ8jfcVwf7Kw58C2OExRQcO1YWpsoZicIo1kJxG7uMT4g3r3iaYJx89e7Q4wM0ox4wXiayDg5uiaPtZqD3obJRvkIw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:670px !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />', '2017-10-08 09:22:02');
INSERT INTO `article_data` VALUES ('245', '<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://yoga.haohaofu.com.cn/static/upload/article/20171007180124_383.gif\" title=\"20171007180124_383.gif\" alt=\"20171007180124_383.gif\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">为庆祝中国传统节日中秋节，10月4日，美国纽约帝国大厦首次为中秋节亮灯。如今的中秋节，正从华人自己过的传统节日，逐渐变成全世界许多国家共同欢度的节日。中秋节是中国的，也是世界的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091359_344.png\" title=\"20171008091359_344.png\" alt=\"20171008091359_344.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">&emsp;说起中秋节，就不得不提世界著名滑板高手埃里克·科斯顿，从某种程度上说，正是这张他手拿月饼、脚踩滑板，飞跃沙发的经典照片，让月饼和中秋在美国开始流行。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091419_136.png\" title=\"20171008091419_136.png\" alt=\"20171008091419_136.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">时至今日，中秋节已经成为除世界滑板日外，最重要的滑手节日之一！而且，由于月饼的超棒口感，滑手们渐渐将吃月饼当成了一件很潮流的事情。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091505_411.png\" title=\"20171008091505_411.png\" alt=\"20171008091505_411.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在美国费城，一场盛大的花灯巡游也为中秋节增色不少。志愿者们踩着挂满近千只灯笼的27辆脚踏三轮车，载着游客和当地民众，在中秋节期间夜游富兰克林大道。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">新加坡、马来西亚、印尼等地也纷纷举办庆祝中秋的传统活动。可以说，华人在哪里，中国味就飘向哪里，十分热闹。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091630_818.png\" title=\"20171008091630_818.png\" alt=\"20171008091630_818.png\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">近几年，中国元素正变得越来越“国际范儿”，出现在全世界很多场合。</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">值得注意的是，以往出现的中国元素大多只是点缀，而现在的中国元素则被越来越多的外国人作为创意的基点、灵感的源泉。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">点缀也好，灵感也罢，有一点却是无可辩驳：中国元素正在加速走向世界…</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#007AAA;font-size:18px;\">中国园林落户欧洲</span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#007AAA;font-size:18px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在偌大的城市寻一处清静之地，放眼亭台楼阁、红砖绿瓦，品一口香茗，余韵绕口。这样的体验，不仅可以在中国实现，在万里之外的比利时，同样可以感受。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091751_302.png\" title=\"20171008091751_302.png\" alt=\"20171008091751_302.png\" /></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在被誉为“比利时最美动植物园”的天堂公园，就有着欧洲最大的中国园林。重峦叠嶂、山清水秀，中国园林浓缩东方意蕴的建筑形式，是中国元素闪耀世界的小小缩影。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">中国武术拉近你我</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在美国纽约曼哈顿中城有一家“咏春堂”武馆，创办者是美国人亚历克斯·里克特，他用10多年的时间，将武馆的学员从最初的15人发展到今天的400多人。他说：“武术不仅是中国的，而且是世界的。”</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091852_382.png\" title=\"20171008091852_382.png\" alt=\"20171008091852_382.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在立陶宛首都维尔纽斯，每年4月的“世界太极和气功日”，都有数百名当地人齐练太极，场面十分壮观。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008091916_187.png\" title=\"20171008091916_187.png\" alt=\"20171008091916_187.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">而在塞尔维亚，如果当地年轻人知道你是中国人，一定会向你展示新学到的中国功夫。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">我们可以毫不客气地说，中国武术是中国向世界贡献的强身健体的宝贵财富。随着中国国力的不断强大，武术热正在席卷全球。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong>中国元素正在融入世界</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">一款游戏圈来众多“洋粉丝”</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">在游戏领域，中国的影响力同样在扩大。一款名为“奇迹暖暖”的游戏，和故宫合作，让暖粉们“穿”上各种故宫博物院的珍藏华服，中华传统文化之美尽显！</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">它也已经走出国门，</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">受到不少国外年轻人的追捧。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092016_577.png\" title=\"20171008092016_577.png\" alt=\"20171008092016_577.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在英国、美国等西方国家，“奇迹暖暖”凭借其丰富独特的服装元素，英伦范儿、摇滚风、中国味，迷倒了一大批外国妹子。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">&emsp;在日本，年轻人也把“奇迹暖暖”当成热门流行游戏。Hello Kitty的品牌商三丽鸥也与“奇迹暖暖”展开了合作。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092046_810.png\" title=\"20171008092046_810.png\" alt=\"20171008092046_810.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在韩国，“奇迹暖暖”一经上架，迅速成为国民少女游戏，多次占据畅销榜前10的位置，受到了众多女性玩家的追捧。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">&emsp;“奇迹暖暖“以一种年轻人喜欢的轻松、快乐的方式传达着中国传统文化，让不同国家、不同地区的年轻人都能深刻体会到中国传统文化之美。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092114_749.png\" title=\"20171008092114_749.png\" alt=\"20171008092114_749.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">截至今年7月，中国自主研发网络游戏市场实际销售收入达到 693.7 亿元。在过去的15年中，全球至少有24家游戏公司实现了10亿美元的估值，这其中有11家来自中国。这</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">表明，过去被外国人视为山寨、盗版的中国游戏产业已经焕然一新</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">一道中餐“征服”美日韩</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">说到中国美食，在世界上绝对是无敌的存在，在美剧里出现最多的镜头可能就是吃中餐了。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092203_828.png\" title=\"20171008092203_828.png\" alt=\"20171008092203_828.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">甚至可以说，中国美食是国人生活智慧与传统文化交融的缩影，也是中外文化交流的纽带。无论是小吃还是大餐，似乎分分钟都能攻陷外国人的味蕾。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092230_268.png\" title=\"20171008092230_268.png\" alt=\"20171008092230_268.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"color:#888888;\">△加拿大沙县小吃</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092252_433.png\" title=\"20171008092252_433.png\" alt=\"20171008092252_433.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"color:#888888;\">△中国煎饼“移民”纽约</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">不久前，黄焖鸡米饭更是一不留神搞出了大事情。</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\">不仅在新加坡、澳大利亚、日本、韩国……黄焖鸡米饭的全球分店已经开出超过6000家！</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" background-color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092333_129.png\" title=\"20171008092333_129.png\" alt=\"20171008092333_129.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">&emsp;&emsp;今年9月10日，黄焖鸡米饭更是登陆美国，在加州塔斯廷市（Tustin）奥兰治县（Orange County），正式开业了！</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092357_235.png\" title=\"20171008092357_235.png\" alt=\"20171008092357_235.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong>一句“你好”沟通世界</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#007AAA;\">微信被顶级博物馆收藏</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#007AAA;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">随着微信用户规模越来越庞大，就连外国人也爱上了微信。去年在美国，微信用户疯涨11倍。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">前不久在英国，曾经收藏苹果iMac G3（主要设计者：Jonathan Ive，1998年）的世界级博物馆——维多利亚与艾伯特博物馆（V&amp;A）宣布，微信被正式纳入永久馆藏。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092447_680.png\" title=\"20171008092447_680.png\" alt=\"20171008092447_680.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">V&amp;A副馆长Tim Reeve表示：“微信是全球社交应用平台的一个缩影，是数字设计藏品中非常重要的新增展品。通过微信，我们可以看到人们交流和使用信息的方式在不断变化。”</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#007AAA;font-size:18px;\">全世界都在学讲中国话</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">当你在花钱上英语补习班时，越来越多外国学生也在参加中文补习班。“中文热”在世界各地悄然兴起，“全世界都在说中国话”已经不再仅仅是一句歌词了。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">9月7日，英国的乔治小王子和其他小朋友一样，开始步入学堂。在学前班上，年仅4岁的乔治王子课业繁重，不仅有英语、数学、芭蕾等课程，还要学说中文。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092542_783.png\" title=\"20171008092542_783.png\" alt=\"20171008092542_783.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">而英国先后两任首相卡梅伦和特雷莎·梅都曾亲自提倡中文学习。卡梅伦更是表示，“我希望英国人能和全世界发展最快的经济体保持联系。我们应该把注意力从传统的法语、德语转移到中文上，学好中文才能在未来生意场上畅通无阻。”</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在俄罗斯，汉语将列入国家统一考试科目。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">在加拿大，学习中文的人数从2011年的27万，猛增到去年的64万。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">&emsp;据统计，海外中文教师缺口量已超过500万，且薪资水平颇高。在美国，中文教师的年收入已突破10万美元；在西欧，年薪在8万欧元左右。中文外教“走红”世界，成为华人又一新兴高薪职业。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">&emsp;专家预测，2020年底，海外学习汉语的人数将达2亿。世界人民学汉语的热潮正成为无法阻挡的新趋势。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><img src=\"/static/upload/article/20171008092638_862.png\" title=\"20171008092638_862.png\" alt=\"20171008092638_862.png\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#CD0000;\">为酷酷的祖国点赞！</span></strong><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" font-size:18px;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><img width=\"345\" src=\"http://img.8htq.com.cn/upload/20160922/image36/147451297736.jpg?wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" height=\"82\" style=\"width:345px;height:82px;\" /></span></strong></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#D82821;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;line-height:22.39px;font-size:14px;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:18px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#C00000;font-weight:normal;\"><strong><img width=\"345\" src=\"http://img.8htq.com.cn/upload/20160922/image33/147451297733.jpg?wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" height=\"75\" style=\"width:345px;height:75px;\" /></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><span style=\"line-height:25.6px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#7B0C00;\"><img src=\"http://yoga.haohaofu.com.cn/static/upload/article/20171008091520_647.gif\" title=\"20171008091520_647.gif\" alt=\"20171008091520_647.gif\" /></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '2017-10-08 09:29:57');
